summary:
Architect and Urban planner from UNLP, Universidad de La Plata, Argentina.

With more than five years of experience in the architecture and constructions field. From the sketches to 3ds image, project management including planning, budget management, and coordination to reach goals within scope and budget, until the execution and coordination of tasks of the build. 
I am able to use industry software programs, such as AutoCAD, 3ds Studio Max, Revit, SketchUp, Adobe, V-ray, among others. During the course of my professional experience, I had the opportunity to get courses to develop my skills. 

Here you can find some of my work: https://www.behance.net/martinaugustocosta
